Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.88,0:01:22.44,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\fsp-1}支离破碎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.84,0:01:27.93,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\fsp-1}爱上他人 又无法入眠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.53,0:01:39.35,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\fsp-1}没有什么普通的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.86,0:01:43.50,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\fsp-1}只是看似如此罢了
